::Dollen::

            Pictures of Starscream, Galvatron, Jetfire and all the other
Decepticons flashed through Dollen's mind.  The pictures of the Decepticon's
transformed into pictures of Predacons.  Then, an image of BrightBlade and
GoldenEye showed up.  Fire.....There was
fire...........Predacons.........Burning........Help........Danger..........
..The Crash......The crash...........Was he dead?????  He couldn't feel his
physical structure.  He had to do something.........The Predacons needed
him........GoldenEye needed him...........Something spoke in his mind, and
he knew this.......He had to help!!!!  He was too young to die, and too
important to the future.  He wanted to talk to GoldenEye, say something to
her, anything.  But, nothing came out.  Then, he managed two words, "Keep
me......................."
